Corporate Senior Associate, Boutique Corporate Firm, Dubai
Corporate Senior Associate, Boutique Corporate Firm, Dubai
Location:  --Dubai
An exciting and rare opportunity has arisen for a mid-senior corporate associate to join a highly ambitious and successful boutique corporate law firm in Dubai. The firm is staffed by lawyers from top US and UK law firms and has an extremely strong pipeline of corporate deals across the region.
Due to the high volume of transactional work our client is now seeking an English qualified lawyer who will have a hands on background in advising on corporate transactions across the Middle East. The Firm is expanding to other jurisdictions in the region and has exciting plans for continued growth. Our client will pay competitive international salary rates.
